ort, are part of the so-called Big 8 group of Global Systemically Important Banks, which the Fed deems crucial to broader financial system risks and imposes higher capital buffer rules as backstop.  The concern stems from the ability of Mythos to find and exploit so-called zero-day vulnerabilities in tech infrastructure, based on relatively simple prompting.", "pubDate": "2026-04-10T20:49:00Z", "displayTime": "2026-04-10T20:49:00Z", "isHosted": false, "bypassModal": false, "previewUrl": "https://finance.yahoo.com/m/1dcf2243-a1cf-3f8f-a3ba-243ef57badb0/anthropic%E2%80%99s-new-ai-model.html", "thumbnail": {"originalUrl": "https://media.zenfs.com/en/Barrons.com/ca83209e28b905bc2f18ecf1cdd98a3b", "originalWidth": 1280, "originalHeight": 640, "caption": "", "resolutions": [{"url": "https://s.yimg.com/uu/api/res/1.2/Dj8WLU7IDlRCub6oPsYECg--~B/aD02NDA7dz0xMjgwO2FwcGlkPXl0YWNoeW9u/https://media.zenfs.com/en/Barrons.com/ca83209e28b905bc2f18ecf1cdd98a3b", "width": 1280, "height": 640, "tag": "original"}, {"url": "https://s.yimg.com/uu/api/res/1.2/eSyD8_jxBPS44YL2z157hg--~B/Zmk9c3RyaW07aD0xMjg7dz0xNzA7YXBwaWQ9eXRhY2h5b24-/https://media.zenfs.com/en/Barrons.com/ca83209e28b905bc2f18ecf1cdd98a3b", "width": 170, "height": 128, "tag": "170x128"}]}, "provider": {"displayName": "Barrons.com", "url": "http://www.barrons.com/", "sourceId": "Barrons.com"}, "canonicalUrl": {"url": "https://www.barrons.com/articles/bessent-powell-anthropic-mythos-cybersecurity-crowdstrike-stock-25ae1cb7?siteid=yhoof2&yptr=yahoo", "site": "finance", "region": "US", "lang": "en-US"}, "clickThroughUrl": null, "metadata": {"editorsPick": false}, "finance": {"premiumFinance": {"isPremiumNews": false, "isPremiumFreeNews": false}}, "storyline": null}}]